# API Products

# Group Products

## List Products [GET /v1/products?filter='{name}'&order='{createdAt}']

Untuk mendapatkan daftar product / item.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Header

            Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2FwaV9pZCI6MywiZXhwIjoxNTUwMDg4NTE0fQ.Jnp0NMZ05zlXs4mKNdbt7cJ4Xwf8mTZrU-PS_eQY-vQ

+ Parameters
    + code: `PR001` (string) - Filtering product by code using method `LIKE`.
    + name: `Tiket Pesawat` (string) - Filtering product by name using method `LIKE`.
    + is_has_tax: true (boolean) - Filtering product by tax having.
    + createdAt: `2021-02-01T13:40:10Z` (timestamp) - Sort / order product by date created.

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body

