## Create Product [POST /v1/product]

Untuk membuat product / item untuk digunakan pada uang muka, pengeluaran, dll.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Header

            Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2FwaV9pZCI6MywiZXhwIjoxNTUwMDg4NTE0fQ.Jnp0NMZ05zlXs4mKNdbt7cJ4Xwf8mTZrU-PS_eQY-vQ

    + Attributes (object)
        + name: `Tiket Pesawat` (string) - Product name.
        + description: `Tiket pesawat untuk perjalanan dinas` (string) - Product Description.
        + isHasTax: true (boolean) - Describe if the product is taxable or not.
        + amount: 750000 (string) - How much amount will be pay for product.
        + coaId: `3e7436b1-adeb-4a85-8676-2968e0cec78c` (string).
        + isActive: true (boolean) - Activate / Disabled the product.

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "message": "Product successfully created."
            }

+ Response 400 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "fail",
                "code": "PRODUCT_CREATE_FAILED",
                "message": "failed to create product",
                "traceId": "5343f4f4-36a3-47cc-afe2-01b37a2063bf"
            }

+ Response 500 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "error",
                "code": "GENERAL_ERROR",
                "message": "Internal Server Error",
                "traceId": "5343f4f4-36a3-47cc-afe2-01b37a2063bf"
            }

## Update Product [PATCH /v1/product/{id}/update]

