    + Header

            Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2FwaV9pZCI6MywiZXhwIjoxNTUwMDg4NTE0fQ.Jnp0NMZ05zlXs4mKNdbt7cJ4Xwf8mTZrU-PS_eQY-vQ
    
    + Attributes (object)
        + name: `Tiket Pesawat` (string) - Product name.
        + description: `Tiket pesawat untuk perjalanan dinas` (string) - Product Description.
